doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1')
    title photoshop

    // build:css styles/styles.css
    //- Check out 'src/bower_components/prism/themes/' for available themes
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='bower_components/prism/themes/prism-tomorrow.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='styles/main.css')
    // endbuild

  body

    article

      section
        h1 photoshop
        h2 sketch & painting
        p tutorial membuat foto dengan efek lukisan cat air dalam nuansa full color

      section
        <img src="gambar/Sherina-121.jpg" class="cool">
        p model "sherina"
      section
        <img src="gambar/awal.png">
        p masukan gambar ke dalam fhotoshop

      section
        <img src="gambar/1.png">
        p klik menu image > adjustment > levels karena gambar hanya memerlukan sedikit koreksi levels pilih auto level


      section
        <img src="gambar/2.png">
        p aktif pada "layer1" ubah nama menjadi "model". Klik menu Filter > Other > High Pass berikan nilai radius 1 pixels, klik OK

      section
       <img src="gambar/3.png">
       p selanjutnya tekan CTRL + ShIFT + U. Ubah mode Blending layer "model" menjadi Overlay

      selection
        <img src="gambar/4.png">
        p tekan ALT + SHIFT + CTRL + E , untuk menggabungkan background dengan model

      selection
        <img src="gambar/4.5.png">
        p duplikat layer1 ubah nama menjadi mcutout lalu masuk ke menu filter > blur > surface blur. atur nilai radius = 20 dan threshold = 15 setelah selesai
      

      section
        <img src="gambar/5.png">
        p masuk ke menu filter galerry > cutout atur parameter sesuai gambar 

      section(data-bespoke-state='emphatic')
        h2 Emphatic Slide!
        h3 Powered by <a href="https://github.com/markdalgleish/bespoke-state">bespoke-state</a>

      section
        h2.bullet Just the beginning...
        hr
        ul
          li Edit <a href="http://jade-lang.com/">Jade</a> markup in <em>'src/index.jade'</em>
          li Edit <a href="http://learnboost.github.io/stylus/">Stylus</a> styles in <em>'src/styles/main.styl'</em>
          li Edit JavaScript in <em>'src/scripts/main.js'</em>
        hr
        ul
          li
            strong Enjoy! :)
            a(href='http://twitter.com/markdalgleish')  -@markdalgleish

